:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_b21c9cb1-8b03-474a-8736-cceafab16a5f" inv:numbering="continue"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_f7a88484-64be-4d7f-9e0a-88bf2326a81e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> listed are for the labelled, declared <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_47c9421b-8eac-4fb6-9cc2-d171db1bb645" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of insulation.</li><li id="_0bda01a3-7007-404c-91e0-6136ecf6ca3e">X = not permitted.</li><li id="_dece0be2-e4ce-4595-99a9-0685ea9113ed">This Table shows wall heights for single <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_53ff3cc4-0dc1-48ce-a733-6406d28cbeba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> dwellings. For two <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_b6059529-6815-4ccc-9e49-849f343d52af" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> (or more) dwellings, add R0.5 to the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_00c48480-6ca0-4e03-b6fb-745b0f964642" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> given in this Table.</li><li id="_9e428dd2-6316-4c9d-bfbd-2a75eca6ab8f">Where an overhang of &gt; 900 mm is used, the values for &gt; 600 to ≤ 900 apply provided no more than 15% of the total opaque wall area of the dwelling (excluding windows/doors) is covered by overhangs &gt; 900 mm.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference>